# Terraform in any service root: infra/hub/, infra/vpc/, infra/rds/, infra/secrets/, infra/worker/, infra/agents/*/, infra/localstack/, etc.
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Variable files often contain secrets — use *.tfvars.example in repo
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!*.tfvars.example

# Do NOT ignore: .terraform.lock.hcl (commit for reproducible applies)
